@laanwj, I was not aware about these other sensitive files.
Don't you think this deserves an issue of its own?
I mean.. I never treated any other file with the same care that I treat wallet.dat, and I guess I'm not the only one. There's either a bug there (leaking sensitive data to logs) or a great need of more clarification for most users, as I don't think I'm the only one that's not aware of such thing...
